722666f-b.text:
(1)
Prince Street, north side, west from and including Mott, to and including Mulberry Streets. The view shows the Roman Catholic Church of St. Patrick.
August 1, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same, showing Prince Street, north side, east from and including Mulberry, to and including Mott Streets. Also shown is Mott Street, at, adjoining and north of the N.E. corner of
Prince Street.
August 28, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
